    "https://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "It's going to be an exciting evening! Here's what to expect: A sneak peek of next season’s performances Special guest appearances by Shakura S'Aida and James Keelaghan Mingle with fellow arts enthusiasts Enjoy light refreshments with treats from Performance Sponsor Pan Chancho Have a chance to win your 2026-27 Grand OnStage subscription with the “Driven to Subscribe Early\" Promotion presented by Van Herpt Auto Group*"
      }
